title: The Burgeoning River
review: A beautiful site as you see the river bulging at one end of the dam and flowing down the other side. Standing on the bridge you see the forest and not so high mountains, you become one with nature.

title: Nice view
review: Kalagadh Dam is inside the Jim Corbett National Park. Its a beautiful place. Its also a breeding ground for lots of aquatic animals and fishes. It also attracts lots of bird species. Definitely a visit if you are going to Jim Corbett national park.

title: Awesome
review: Awesome place it is. Inside the Jim Corbett National Park, it is one of the famous must see in here. The landscape and nature is at its beauty around here.

title: Awesome Place
review: You just feel like getting lost in the scenic beauty of this divine place. I loved spending time here.

title: good place  beautiful lake
review: the dam id build on ramganga river inside corbett national park ... created a long lake ... the famous dhikala water reserve is because of this dam ... looks amazing when u visit dhikala...

title: Beautiful Scenic Dam
review: Kalagarh Dam is adjacent to Jim Corbett Park . Elephants can be seen roaming around. Boat ride upstream reservoir would provide rare scenic view of wild animals of Jim Corbett Park.

title: A nice place for family picnic...
review: This is a place with some awesome views... The dam is prominently located and the entire ambience is very peaceful and amazing...
